{"tid":1681563,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"醍醐灌頂 - 古德明","createTime":"2019-10-29T13:37:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-29T14:51:09.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"76f2d679f7eeb2428db87ade6341437e4fef6690","tid":1681563,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T13:37:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E5%8F%A4%E5%BE%B7%E6%98%8E/daily/article/20191029/20795547/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E5%258F%25A4%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E6%2598%258E%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191029%2F20795547%2F&d=WC8zRIkQRph3x4hQUB%2Bsg60IH4hhGWFtD%2BQErH2Rjq0%3D&h=7f983aa2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E5%258F%25A4%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E6%2598%258E%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191029%2F20795547%2F&h=f16e6ba2\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E5%8F%A4%E5%BE%B7%E6%98%8E/daily/article/20191029/20795547/</a><br />\n<br />\n醍醐灌頂 - 古德明<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20191029/large/1572247296_c5dd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20191029%2Flarge%2F1572247296_c5dd.jpg&h=a7614a47&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n十月二十日，三十五萬港人上街反暴政，黑警出動水砲車，以藍色胡椒毒液襲人，途經尖沙嘴清真寺，突然停下，向寺門前幾個站着聊天者狂噴毒液，那幾人猝不及備，渾身濕透，其中一人竟然是印度協會前主席毛漢。<br />\n<br />\n毛漢事後憤憤不平說：「我們幾個人沒戴面罩，沒持雨傘，沒穿黑衣，根本不是反政府者裝束，怎麼襲擊我們？我當時全身有如火燒，眼睛將近半小時張不開，警察是這樣對付一個七十三歲老人的嗎？行政長官鄭月娥曾打電話向我道歉，但街上很多人和我一樣無理被襲，誰向他們表示歉意？警察現在完全無法無天，香港快要成為警察國家了！」他說得好，但古人說得更好：「多行無禮，必自及也。」<br />\n<br />\n二零一五年，即梁振英政府鎮壓民主佔領運動之後，毛漢獲梁振英頒授行政長官服務獎狀，與梁合照，春風滿面；今年七月二十日，即元朗黑警與黑幫合力進剿市民前一天，他還出席撐警大會，與陳百祥、「肥媽」等賤戲子一起，講臺上慷慨陳詞。我不是幸災樂禍，但見暴政壓迫他人，而曰「與我無干」，已是令人齒冷，何況助桀為虐，自食其果，不亦宜乎。<br />\n<br />\n當然，毛漢現在能想到「街上很多人和我一樣無理被襲」，這推己及人情懷總算難得。希望他從此能分清善惡，擇善固執，則那胡椒毒水，實無異於灌頂醍醐。 <br />\n<br />\n古德明<br />\n電郵 :appledailykoo@gmail.com"},{"pid":"04436353afff2b56f1af763846a1d705a38aee3b","tid":1681563,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T13:38:21.000Z","msg":"地政處就元朗中資銀行 僭建圍板非法佔用土地發出清拆令<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1681312\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1681312</a><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"773fed41c23793f5214f3002c7b005627a604919","tid":1681563,"uid":20554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T13:39:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65d3b5c4ddf724c8757b75addee1722fbfb2e03d","tid":1681563,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T13:42:26.000Z","msg":"三個字講完：「抵撚死！」"},{"pid":"11699b93c433b5efeda9edc1cc2933c312493562","tid":1681563,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T13:47:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>主線速遞</strong></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n-------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">星期六 11 &middot; 2 </span><br />\n求援國際 堅守自治</strong></span><br />\n- 15:00 維園流水式集會<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1678270/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1678270/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">星期六 11 &middot; 9 </span><br />\n柏林圍牆倒塌30周年集會</strong></span><br />\n- 19:30 中環愛丁堡廣場<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1678139/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1678139/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: